ffset_DST    = +2\n| registration_plate = [[Vehicle registration plates of Austria|IL]]\n| postal_code_type   = [[List of postal codes in Austria|Postal code]]\n| postal_code        = 6408\n| area_code_type = [[Telephone numbers in Austria|Area code]]\n| area_code      = 05238\n| website   = [http://www.pettnau.at www.pettnau.at]\n| footnotes = \n}}\n'''Pettnau''' is a municipality in the district of [[Innsbruck-Land]] in the [[Austria]]n state of [[Tyrol (state)|Tyrol]] located 16.7&nbsp;km west of [[Innsbruck]] north of the [[Inn River]] between [[Telfs]] and [[Zirl]]. It has seven parts and was founded around 1291.\n\n==Population==\n{{Historical populations\n|align=left\n|1869|313\n|1880|280\n|1890|260\n|1900|261\n|1910|279\n|1923|264\n|1934|347\n|1939|334\n|1951|367\n|1961|386\n|1971|626\n|1981|761\n|1991|808\n|2001|977\n|2011|893\n}}\n{{clear left}}\n\n==Sights==\nWorth seeing in Pettnau are the ''St. Georgskirche'', which has been built in 1090 and the ''Mellaunerhof'', the oldest inn in the Tyrol, as well as the sculpture garden of Bernhard Witsch.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Pettnau}}\n\n{{Cities and towns in Innsbruck-Land (district)}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Innsbruck-Land District]]\n\n\n{{Tyrol-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement\n| name            = Pettnau\n| native_name     = \n| settlement_type = \n<!-- Images     -->\n| image_skyline   = Unterpettnau.jpg\n| imagesize       = \n| image_caption   = \n| image_shield    = Wappen at pettnau.png\n| shield_size     = 80x110px\n| shield_link     = \n<!-- Maps           -->\n| pushpin_map         = Austria\n| pushpin_mapsize     = 270\n| pushpin_map_caption = Location within Austria\n| image_map           = \n| mapsize             = \n| map_alt             =\n| map_caption         = Location within Innsbruck Land district\n<!-- Location    -->\n| coordinates       = {{coord|47|17|31|N|11|09|36|E|display=inline,tit