80\n|1890|260\n|1900|261\n|1910|279\n|1923|264\n|1934|347\n|1939|334\n|1951|367\n|1961|386\n|1971|626\n|1981|761\n|1991|808\n|2001|977\n|2011|893\n}}\n{{clear left}}\n\n==Sights==\nWorth seeing in Pettnau are the ''St. Georgskirche'', which has been built in 1090 and the ''Mellaunerhof'', the oldest inn in the Tyrol, as well as the sculpture garden of Bernhard Witsch.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Pettnau}}\n\n{{Cities and towns in Innsbruck-Land (district)}}\n\n[[Category:Cities and towns in Innsbruck-Land District]]\n\n\n{{Tyrol-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pettnau"}
{"title_page": "Pettend, Fej\u00e9r", "text_new": "{{Infobox settlement <!--more fields are available for this Infobox--See Template:Infobox Settlement-->\n|subdivision_type = [[Countries of the world|Country]]\n|subdivision_name       = {{HUN}}\n|timezone=[[Central European Time|CET]]\n|utc_offset=+1\n|timezone_DST=[[Central European Summer Time|CEST]]\n|utc_offset_DST=+2\n\n|\nofficial_name=Pettend|\nmap=[[Image:FejerMegye.png|center|thumb|275px|Location of Fej\u00e9r county in Hungary]]|\nsubdivision_type1=[[Counties of Hungary|County]]|\nsubdivision_name1=[[Fejer County]]|\narea_total_km2=5.98|\npopulation_total=171|\npopulation_as_of=2004|\npopulation_density_km2=28.59|\npostal_code_type=[[Postal code]]|\npostal_code= 2475|\narea_code=22|\npushpin_map            =Hungary \n|pushpin_label_position = <!-- the position of the pushpin label: left, right, top, bottom, none -->\n|pushpin_map_caption    =Location of Pettend\n|pushpin_mapsize        =\n|coordinates            = {{coord|47.26269|18.71614|region:HU|display=inline,title}}\n}}\n\n'''Pettend''' is a village in [[Fej\u00e9r County]], [[Hungary]].\n\n== External links ==\n*http://www.terkepcentrum.hu/index.asp?go=map&mid=7&tid=21926\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pettend, Fejer}}\n[[Category:Populated places in Fej\u00e9r County]]\n\n\n{{Fejer-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox settlement <!--more fields are available for this Infobox--See Template:Infobox Settlement-->\n|subdivision_type = [[Countries of the world|Country]]\n|subdivision_name       = {{HUN}}\n|timezone=[[Central European Time|CET]]\n|utc_offset=+1\n|timezone_DST=[[Central European Summer Time|CEST]]\n|utc_offset_DST=+2\n\n|\nofficial_name=Pettend|\nmap=[[Image:FejerMegye.png|center|thumb|275px|Location of Fej\u00e9r county in Hungary]]|\nsubdivision_type1=[[Counties of Hungary|County]]|\nsubdivision_name1=[[Fejer County]]|\narea_total_km2=5.98|\npopulation_total=171|\npopulation_as_of=2004|\npopulation_density_km2=28.59|\npostal_code_type=[[Postal code]]|\npostal_code= 2475|\narea_code=22|\npushpin_map            =Hungary \n|pushpin_label_position = <!-- the position of the pushpin label: left, right, top, bottom, none -->\n|pushpin_map_caption    =Location of Pettend\n|pushpin_mapsize        =\n|coordinates            = {{coord|47.26269|18.71614|region:HU|display=inline,title}}\n}}\n\n'''Pettend''' is a village in [[Fej\u00e9r County]], [[Hungary]].\n\n== External links ==\n*http://www.terkepcentrum.hu/index.asp?go=map&mid=7&tid=21926\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Pettend, Fejer}}\n[[Category:Populated places in Fej\u00e9r County]]\n\n\n{{Fejer-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eExternal links:add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pettend,_Fej%C3%A9r"}
{"title_page": "Pettend", "text_new": "{{for|the village in [[Fej\u00e9r County]]|Pettend, Fej\u00e9r}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- General information -->\n|name                   =Pettend\n|settlement_type        =Village\n|image_shield           =\n|image_flag             =\n<!-- Pushpin map -->\n|pushpin_map            =Hungary\n|pushpin_map_caption    =Location of Pettend in Hungary\n<!-- Political information -->\n|subdivision_type       =Country\n|subdivision_name       =[[Hungary]]\n|subdivision_type1      =[[List of regions of Hungary|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1      =[[{{Hungarian county region|Baranya}}]]\n|subdivision_type2      =[[Counties of Hungary|County]]\n|subdivision_name2      ={{Hungarian county link|Baranya}}\n|leader_title           =Mayor\n|leader_name            =Lakatos S\u00e1ndor<ref>{{cite web  |language=hu |url=http://www.valasztas.hu/dyn/ov10/outroot/onktjk1/02/tjk02216.htm |title=Pettend telep\u00fcl\u00e9si v\u00e1laszt\u00e1s eredm\u00e9nyei |date=3 October 2010 |accessdate=15 December 2011 | publisher=Orsz\u00e1gos V\u00e1laszt\u00e1si }}</ref>\n<!-- Geographical information -->\n|area_magnitude         =1 E6\n|area_footnotes         =<ref name=\"ksh_cite_area\">[http://www.ksh.hu/apps/!cp.hnt2.telep?nn=29762 Pettend] at the [[Hungarian Central Statistical Office]] (Hungarian).</ref>\n|coordinates            ={{coord|46.00086|N|17.69931|E|region:HU|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n<!-- Demographical information -->\n|postal_code            =7972\n|postal_code_type       =[[Postal code]]\n|area_code              =+36 \n|area_code_type         =[[Telephone numbers in Hungary|Area code]]\n|timezone               =[[Central European Time|CET]]\n|utc_offset             =+1\n|timezone_DST           =[[Central European Summer Time|CEST]]\n|utc_offset_DST         =+2\n|total_type             =Total\n|population_total       =149\n|population_density_km2 =auto\n|population_density_urban_km2 =auto\n|population_density_metro_km2 =auto\n|population_as_of       =2012\n|population_footnotes   =<ref name=\"ksh_cite_population\">[http://www.ksh.hu/apps/!cp.hnt2.telep?nn=29762 Pettend] at the [[Hungarian Central Statistical Office]] (Hungarian). 2012</ref>\n\n|blank_name             =[[Hungarian Central Statistical Office|KSH code]]\n|blank_info             =29762<ref name=\"ksh_cite_area\">[http://www.ksh.hu/apps/!cp.hnt2.telep?nn=29762 Pettend] at the [[Hungarian Central Statistical Office]] (Hungarian).</ref>\n|website                ={{wikidata|property|P856}}\n}}\n\n'''Pettend''' ({{lang-hr|Petan}}<ref>{{cite web |url=http://hrcak.srce.hr/file/11541 |title= Folia onomastica croatica 14/2005.|date= |accessdate=25 July 2012 |author=  | publisher= |work=\u017divko Mandi\u0107: Hrvatska imena naseljenih mjesta u Mad\u017earskoj |format= pdf |language=hr}}</ref>) is a village in Szigetv\u00e1ri district of [[Baranya County]], Hungary. As of 2012 it had a population of 149.\n\nPettend lies to the south of the confluence of the [[Szigetv\u00e1r]] and [[Kistam\u00e1si]] rivers.\n\n== History ==\nThe first mention of Pettend was in 1330, spelled ''Petend'', and assigned to the estate of Peter Siklosi. In 1449 the land was divided between three families of [[landed gentry]], Thuz, Letai, and  Sz\u0151cs\u00e9nyi. In 1493 the estate was bought by Mih\u00e1lyn\u00e9 Kornis, that is, the wife of Mih\u00e1ly Kornis.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://utazom.com/magyarorszag/del-dunantul/a-drava-mellek/barcs-es-a-dravamellek/pettend-terkep|title=Pettend|publisher=Utazom.com|accessdate=5 May 2015|language=Hungarian}}</ref> In the 18th century, Count [[Laszl\u00f3 N\u00e1dasdy]] inhabited the area. In the 20th century, with changes in boundaries, it became part of [[Somogy County]].\n\n== Notable people ==\n* [[Gy\u00f6rffy Gy\u00f6rgy]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{commons category|Pettend (Baranya County)|Pettend}}\n\n{{Baranya}}\n\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Towns in Hungary]]\n[[Category:Populated places in Baranya County]]\n\n\n{{Baranya-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{for|the village in [[Fej\u00e9r County]]|Pettend, Fej\u00e9r}}\n{{Infobox settlement\n<!-- General information -->\n|name                   =Pettend\n|settlement_type        =Village\n|image_shield           =\n|image_flag             =\n<!-- Pushpin map -->\n|pushpin_map            =Hungary\n|pushpin_map_caption    =Location of Pettend in Hungary\n<!-- Political information -->\n|subdivision_type       =Country\n|subdivision_name       =[[Hungary]]\n|subdivision_type1      =[[List of regions of Hungary|Region]]\n|subdivision_name1      =[[{{Hungarian county region|Baranya}}]]\n|subdivision_type2      =[[Counties of Hungary|County]]\n|subdivision_name2      ={{Hungarian county link|Baranya}}\n|leader_title           =Mayor\n|leader_name            =Lakatos S\u00e1ndor<ref>{{cite web  |language=hu |url=http://www.valasztas.hu/dyn/ov10/outroot/onktjk1/02/tjk02216.htm |title=Pettend telep\u00fcl\u00e9si v\u00e1laszt\u00e1s eredm\u00e9nyei |date=3 October 2010 |accessdate=15 December 2011 | publisher=Orsz\u00e1gos V\u00e1laszt\u00e1si }}</ref>\n<!-- Geographical information -->\n|area_magnitude         =1 E6\n|area_footnotes         =<ref name=\"ksh_cite_area\">[http://www.ksh.hu/apps/!cp.hnt2.telep?nn=29762 Pettend] at the [[Hungarian Central Statistical Office]] (Hungarian). </ref>\n|coordinates            ={{coord|46.00086|N|17.69931|E|region:HU|format=dms|display=inline,title}}\n<!-- Demographical information -->\n|postal_code            =7972\n|postal_code_type       =[[Postal code]]\n|area_code              =+36 \n|area_code_type         =[[Telephone numbers in Hungary|Area code]]\n|timezone               =[[Central European Time|CET]]\n|utc_offset             =+1\n|timezone_DST           =[[Central European Summer Time|CEST]]\n|utc_offset_DST         =+2\n|total_type             =Total\n|population_total       =149\n|population_density_km2 =auto\n|population_density_urban_km2 =auto\n|population_dens